@host = http://localhost:8080

### Health check (NFR-03 liveness)
GET {{host}}/health

### P1 / Block — R04 (+40) first-time benef >N500K + R05 (+30) new device + R03 (+50) watchlisted receiver = 120
POST {{host}}/api/screening/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionRef": "TX-P1",
  "customerId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "type": "InterBankTransferNip",
  "direction": "Outflow",
  "channel": "Adspire",
  "amount": 750000,
  "senderAccount": "0011223344",
  "receiverAccount": "0099887766",
  "receiverBvn": "22222222222",
  "isNewDevice": true,
  "minutesSinceFirstLogin": 5,
  "isFirstTimeBeneficiary": true
}

### P2 / RequireMfa — R04 (+40) + R05 (+30) = 70, clean receiver
POST {{host}}/api/screening/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionRef": "TX-P2",
  "customerId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "type": "IntraBankTransfer",
  "direction": "Outflow",
  "channel": "Adspire",
  "amount": 750000,
  "senderAccount": "0011223344",
  "receiverAccount": "0055667788",
  "isNewDevice": true,
  "minutesSinceFirstLogin": 5,
  "isFirstTimeBeneficiary": true
}

### P3 / Flag — R04 (+40) first-time beneficiary >N500K only
POST {{host}}/api/screening/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionRef": "TX-P3",
  "customerId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "type": "IntraBankTransfer",
  "direction": "Outflow",
  "channel": "Adspire",
  "amount": 600000,
  "senderAccount": "0011223344",
  "receiverAccount": "0055667788",
  "isFirstTimeBeneficiary": true
}

### Clean / Allow — R14 (-5) recurring beneficiary, floored to 0
POST {{host}}/api/screening/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionRef": "TX-CLEAN",
  "customerId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "type": "IntraBankTransfer",
  "direction": "Outflow",
  "channel": "Adspire",
  "amount": 25000,
  "senderAccount": "0011223344",
  "receiverAccount": "0055667788",
  "successfulTransfersToBeneficiary": 5
}

### P1 / Block via velocity + balance — R02 (+50) >5 transfers/10min + R08 (+35) >80% of balance = 85
POST {{host}}/api/screening/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionRef": "TX-VELOCITY",
  "customerId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "type": "IntraBankTransfer",
  "direction": "Outflow",
  "channel": "Adspire",
  "amount": 90000,
  "senderAccount": "0011223344",
  "receiverAccount": "0055667788",
  "history": {
    "outboundTransfersLast10Min": 6,
    "cumulativeOutflowToday": 90000,
    "openingBalanceToday": 100000
  }
}

### P1 / Block — internal blacklist sender (R09 +100, cannot be offset)
POST {{host}}/api/screening/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionRef": "TX-BLACKLIST",
  "customerId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "type": "IntraBankTransfer",
  "direction": "Outflow",
  "channel": "Adspire",
  "amount": 10000,
  "senderAccount": "0011223344",
  "senderBvn": "BLACKLISTED-BVN",
  "receiverAccount": "0055667788"
}
